  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_0' aria-label=\" M/s U.P. Asbestos Limited versus State of Rajasthan & Others pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('0','2025','2025_9_1419_1489','2025INSC1154'); ><font size='4'> <strong>M/S U.P. ASBESTOS LIMITED<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>STATE OF RAJASTHAN & OTHERS </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 9 S.C.R. 1419</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 1154</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010008922025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : B.V. NAGARATHNA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, K.V. VISWANATHAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Issue arose as regards the validity of the Notification No. S.O.377, dated 09.03.2007, issued by the Government of Rajasthan in exercise of its powers conferred by s.8(3) of the Rajasthan Value Added Tax Act, 2003 granting exemption from payment of Value Added Tax on cement sheets and bricks, manufactured in the State of Rajasthan, having contents of fly ash 25% or more by weight subject to specific conditions, is violative of Art. 304(a) of the Constitution of India being discriminatory vis-&agrave;-vis goods imported from outside the State of Rajasthan;<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 24-09-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 3577/2008</font>  <span style='color:#212F3D' > | Direction Issue :</span><font color='green'> Appeals allowed and posted for directions.</font> <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_9_1419_1489','2025INSC1154','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('0','2025','2025_9_1419_1489','2025INSC1154','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('0','2025','2025_9_1419_1489','2025INSC1154');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('0','2025','2025_9_1419_1489','2025INSC1154','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
